Package com.ephesoft.dcma.workflows.service

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BatchInstanceProgressService
    Fetches Progress of batch instance
    CleanErrorJobService
    This interface represents a Service that cleans the running job tables.
    DeploymentService
    This interface represents a service to deploy all the existing process definitions, check if a workflow is deployed and to create and deploy custom process definitions for a batch class.
    InactiveServerResumeService
    This interface represents a service for resuming tasks of failed servers.
    PickUpService
    This interface represents a service for pick up of batches for execution.
    PluginWorkflowCreationService
    This interface represents a service to write process definitions for a plugin.
    ProcessCapacityService
    This interface represents a service that gives the details about Processing Capacity of the server.
    RestartBatchService
    This interface represents the service for restart of a batch.
    WorkflowCreationService
    This interface represents a service to create a BPMN XML for a module or a batch class.
    WorkflowService
    This interface represents the service for workflow execution.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    JobExecutorInitializer
    This class represents a listener to the start/refresh of the server.
